Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.40,0:02:06.30,Default,scu,0,0,0,,This is Mr. Delphy of the Federal\N Bureau of Prohibition from Chicago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.40,0:02:06.30,通用720日文-ja,scu,0,0,0,,シカゴから来た連邦取締官のデルフィ氏だ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.79,0:02:12.40,Default,scu,0,0,0,,He'll be keeping the peace in\N this city from now on in my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.79,0:02:12.80,通用720日文-ja,scu,0,0,0,,今後は私に代わって 彼がこの町の平和を守ることになる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.10,0:02:15.33,Default,rep,0,0,0,,Mr. Delphy, why have you come to this town?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.10,0:02:15.52,通用720日文-ja,rep,0,0,0,,デルフィさん なぜこの町へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.67,0:02:18.74,Default,del,0,0,0,,There's a rotten stench in this town,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.67,0:02:18.74,通用720日文-ja,del,0,0,0,,この町には 悪臭が漂っている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.74,0:02:21.80,Default,del,0,0,0,,and it's coming from the mafia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.74,0:02:21.80,通用720日文-ja,del,0,0,0,,そしてその匂いの元はマフィア共だ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.80,0:02:25.79,Default,del,0,0,0,,I'm here to end the age of the\N police serving as their faithful dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.80,0:02:25.92,通用720日文-ja,del,0,0,0,,警察が奴等の犬であった時代は私が終わらせる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.60,0:02:31.48,Default,rep,0,0,0,,What exactly do you mean by the mafia?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.60,0:02:31.48,通用720日文-ja,rep,0,0,0,,マフィアって具体的には?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.48,0:02:33.55,Default,del,0,0,0,,First, the Fango family.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.48,0:02:33.55,通用720日文-ja,del,0,0,0,,まずは ファンゴ ファミリー
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.95,0:02:38.34,Default,del,0,0,0,,Fango became don in place of Orco,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.95,0:02:38.34,通用720日文-ja,del,0,0,0,,オルコに変わってドンとなったファンゴは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.34,0:02:42.31,Default,del,0,0,0,,and is now working with influential\N people in the city to expand his power.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.34,0:02:42.31,通用720日文-ja,del,0,0,0,,町の有力者と手を結んで 勢力を広げている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.90,0:02:51.94,Default,del,0,0,0,,Then there's the Island, their home base.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.90,0:02:51.94,通用720日文-ja,del,0,0,0,,そして 奴等のアジトである アイランド
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.48,0:02:54.99,Default,del,0,0,0,,It's become a hive for evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.48,0:02:54.99,通用720日文-ja,del,0,0,0,,あそここそが 悪の巣窟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.03,0:02:57.83,Default,del,0,0,0,,I'm going to sweep it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.03,0:02:57.83,通用720日文-ja,del,0,0,0,,私が一掃してみせる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.44,0:03:03.71,Default,del,0,0,0,,Next, the Vanetti family that has\N controlled this city for many years.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.44,0:03:03.71,通用720日文-ja,del,0,0,0,,次に この町を古くから牛耳るヴァネッティ ファミリー
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.06,0:03:06.66,Default,rep,0,0,0,,They finally put an end to their internal feud, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.06,0:03:06.66,通用720日文-ja,rep,0,0,0,,内部抗争がやっと終わりましたね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.18,0:03:12.07,Default,del,0,0,0,,Right now, the acting don of the Vanetti \Nfamily is Vincent's eldest son, Nero.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.18,0:03:12.07,通用720日文-ja,del,0,0,0,,今や実質的なドンはヴィンセントの長男 ネロだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.85,0:03:16.40,Default,del,0,0,0,,The moonshine they make, Lawless Heaven,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.85,0:03:16.40,通用720日文-ja,del,0,0,0,,奴等が密造してるローレス ヘブンは
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.40,0:03:19.85,Default,del,0,0,0,,has been fetching high prices\N domestically and internationally of late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.40,0:03:19.85,通用720日文-ja,del,0,0,0,,近頃国内外で高値で取引されている
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.69,0:03:26.55,Default,rep,0,0,0,,Nero's a popular guy around here though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.69,0:03:26.55,通用720日文-ja,rep,0,0,0,,でも ネロはこの町の人気者ですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:28.54,Default,rep,0,0,0,,Much more popular than you cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:28.54,通用720日文-ja,rep,0,0,0,,警察よりずっとね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:31.91,Default,del,0,0,0,,They're trash, sucking out the blood of law-abiding citizens.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:31.91,通用720日文-ja,del,0,0,0,,奴等は 市民の生き血を吸うクズ共だ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.47,0:03:34.61,Default,del,0,0,0,,I'm going to unmask the beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.47,0:03:34.61,通用720日文-ja,del,0,0,0,,今に化けの皮を剥がしてやる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.62,0:03:37.72,通用720日文-ja,del,0,0,0,,両ファミリーの勢力争いで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.62,0:03:40.69,Default,del,0,0,0,,The power struggle between the two families \Nis endangering public order in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.72,0:03:40.69,通用720日文-ja,del,0,0,0,,町の治安は著しく悪化している
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.95,0:03:42.50,通用720日文-ja,del,0,0,0,,私は...いや
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.95,0:03:46.05,Default,del,0,0,0,,I... No, we of the police will first crack \Ndown on the brewing of moonshine,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.50,0:03:46.05,通用720日文-ja,del,0,0,0,,我々警察は まず密造酒を取り締まり
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:48.26,Default,del,0,0,0,,cutting off their source of income.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:48.26,通用720日文-ja,del,0,0,0,,奴等の収入源を断つ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.26,0:03:50.66,通用720日文-ja,del,0,0,0,,そして 善良な市民の為
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.26,0:03:52.87,Default,del,0,0,0,,Then, for the good people of this city, \Nwe will eradicate every one—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:52.87,通用720日文-ja,del,0,0,0,,必ず奴等を一掃することを...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.28,0:03:55.72,Default,ner,0,0,0,,What a blowhard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.28,0:03:55.72,通用720日文-ja,ner,0,0,0,,暑苦しい野郎だ
