Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.52,0:05:55.84,通用720日文-ja,del,0,0,0,,必ず潰してやるとな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.36,0:06:08.69,Default,cor,0,0,0,,You even dug up info on his family?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.36,0:06:08.69,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,家族のことまで調べ上げるとはね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.75,0:06:14.50,Default,cor,0,0,0,,You've grown comfortable in the mafia...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.75,0:06:14.50,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,すっかりマフィアが板についてきたじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.60,0:06:22.37,Default,tig,0,0,0,,That big-nosed freak...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.60,0:06:22.37,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,あの鼻デカ野郎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:25.79,Default,nero,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:25.79,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,どうした
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.94,0:06:34.73,Default,nero,0,0,0,,"Delphy exposes multiple\N establishments selling bootleg liquor."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.94,0:06:34.73,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,デルフィン氏、密造酒販売店を連日摘発する
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.52,0:06:37.58,Default,tig,0,0,0,,He's messing with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.52,0:06:37.94,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,舐めやがって
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.32,0:06:42.06,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Nero, more and more bars are passing on buying our liquor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.32,0:06:42.06,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,ネロ 酒の仕入れを渋る店が増えて来てる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:46.67,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Fire two or three rounds into big-nose's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:46.67,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,この鼻デカの家に二三発打ち込め
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.91,0:06:49.06,Default,nero,0,0,0,,If that doesn't work, rub him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.91,0:06:49.06,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,それで駄目なら やっちまえ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.06,0:06:53.06,花語製作通用-ja,,0,0,0,,本字幕由✿花語&千夏字幕組✿共同製作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.29,0:06:50.67,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Hey, Nero.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.29,0:06:50.67,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,おい ネロ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.18,0:06:54.96,Default,bar,0,0,0,,It's really affecting him...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.18,0:06:54.96,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,大分 引きずってるな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.42,0:06:57.00,Default,tig,0,0,0,,What do you expect?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.42,0:06:57.00,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,しょうがねだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.00,0:07:06.46,Default,av,0,0,0,,Nice weather, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.00,0:07:06.46,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,いい天気だな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:09.40,Default,av,0,0,0,,Want to go for a drive?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:09.40,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,ドライブでも行くか?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:15.68,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I've decided to never\N get in a car you're driving again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.28,0:07:15.68,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,悪いが お前の運転する車には二度と乗らねって決めってんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.88,0:07:31.87,Default,av,0,0,0,,Fango will make a move soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.88,0:07:31.87,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,ファンゴはそのうち仕掛けてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.69,0:07:35.71,Default,av,0,0,0,,We'd best move cautiously from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.69,0:07:35.71,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,これからは 慎重に動いたほうがいい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.80,0:07:40.77,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I'm the only one left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.80,0:07:40.77,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,もう俺しかいね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.18,0:07:44.39,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I have to protect the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.18,0:07:44.39,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,俺がファミリを守るんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.74,0:07:49.54,Default,nero,0,0,0,,To make that happen, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.74,0:07:49.54,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,そのためなら 俺は
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.11,0:07:55.56,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Will you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.11,0:07:55.56,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,ついてきてくれるか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.10,0:07:57.94,Default,av,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.98,0:08:07.67,Default,cer,0,0,0,,I never thought {\i1}you'd{\i0} join the mafia, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.98,0:08:07.67,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,しっかし お前がマフィアなるとはな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:09.58,Default,cer,0,0,0,,It's unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:09.58,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,まさかの展開だぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:13.29,Default,cer,0,0,0,,"I hate the mafia" used to be your tune.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:13.29,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,マフィアは嫌いなんだとか 言ってたくせによ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.14,0:08:15.85,Default,cor,0,0,0,,I still hate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.14,0:08:15.85,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,今でも嫌いさ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.41,0:08:18.37,Default,cer,0,0,0,,Corteo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.41,0:08:18.37,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,コルテオ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.90,0:08:22.42,Default,cer,0,0,0,,The truth is, Fango wants you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.90,0:08:22.42,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,実はファンゴさんがお前をほしがってんだわ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:25.74,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,ここだけの話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:27.96,Default,cer,0,0,0,,This doesn't leave this room,\N but I hear Prohibition's ending soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.74,0:08:27.96,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,禁酒法は近々終わるらしい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:31.57,Default,cer,0,0,0,,Someone heard a bigshot talking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:31.57,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,どっかのお偉いさんから聞いた情報だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.10,0:08:35.62,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,そうなるや 誰でも簡単に買えるようになる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.10,0:08:37.07,Default,cer,0,0,0,,Then anyone will be able to buy it with no problem just like before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.62,0:08:37.07,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,昔みてぇにな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:40.60,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,ファンゴさんは そん時に備えて
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:42.94,Default,cer,0,0,0,,Fango wants some really good booze to prepare for that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.60,0:08:42.94,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,まじで旨い酒を欲しがってる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.90,0:08:46.98,Default,cer,0,0,0,,That's why he needs you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.90,0:08:46.98,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,そこでお前の力が必要って訳だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:50.31,Default,cer,0,0,0,,Having someone like him\N acknowledge you is pretty amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:50.31,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,あの人に認められるなんて すげぇじゃねか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:53.78,Default,cor,0,0,0,,I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:53.78,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,辞めとくと
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.78,0:08:58.10,Default,cer,0,0,0,,What?! Why? It's your chance to be rich!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.78,0:08:58.10,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,なんでだ 金持ちになれるチャンスなんだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.64,0:09:11.94,Default,del,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.64,0:09:11.94,通用720日文-ja,del,0,0,0,,本当だろうな?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.14,0:09:14.94,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Yeah, I swear to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.14,0:09:15.16,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,神に誓うぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:18.51,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Don't worry. This isn't a trade-off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:18.51,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,安心しろ こりゃ取引じゃね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.76,0:09:23.67,Default,fan,0,0,0,,It's just a tip.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.76,0:09:23.67,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,ただの情報提供だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:25.74,Default,cor,0,0,0,,What? The Lodge is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:25.74,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,へ ロッジが...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.12,0:09:28.36,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Delphy's investigating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.12,0:09:28.36,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,デルフィの捜査が入った
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.36,0:09:29.97,Default,tig,0,0,0,,That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.36,0:09:29.97,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,あの野郎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.35,0:09:33.18,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Take out his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.35,0:09:33.18,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,奴の家族をやれ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.30,0:09:35.86,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Can't we just take him out?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.30,0:09:35.86,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,本人だけで十分だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.86,0:09:36.76,Default,av,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.86,0:09:36.76,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,いやだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.50,0:09:41.11,Default,av,0,0,0,,Then someone else would pick up the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.50,0:09:41.11,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,それじゃ 誰かが捜査を引き継ぐだけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.55,0:09:43.31,Default,nero,0,0,0,,He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.55,0:09:43.52,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.72,0:09:46.56,Default,nero,0,0,0,,We need Delphy himself to call it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.72,0:09:46.56,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,デルフィ自身に捜査を打ち切らせるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.57,0:09:49.01,Default,del,0,0,0,,Let's take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.57,0:09:49.01,通用720日文-ja,del,0,0,0,,休憩にしよう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.60,0:09:53.05,Default,cop,0,0,0,,That reminds me. I'm taking my family out for a picnic soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.60,0:09:53.05,通用720日文-ja,cop,0,0,0,,そういや 今度家族連れてピクニックへ行くんですが
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.05,0:09:54.07,Default,cop,0,0,0,,Want to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.05,0:09:54.07,通用720日文-ja,cop,0,0,0,,どうです
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.52,0:09:57.20,Default,del,0,0,0,,No, I'd like to, but I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.52,0:09:57.20,通用720日文-ja,del,0,0,0,,いいえ 行きたいが さすがに無理だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.20,0:09:58.43,Default,cop,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.20,0:09:58.43,通用720日文-ja,cop,0,0,0,,ですよね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.43,0:10:01.22,Default,del,0,0,0,,I'd love to get out with the family soon, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.43,0:10:01.22,通用720日文-ja,del,0,0,0,,そろそろ 家族揃って出かけたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.22,0:10:02.68,Default,cop,0,0,0,,I'll invite you next time, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.22,0:10:02.68,通用720日文-ja,cop,0,0,0,,まだ 誘いますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.68,0:10:03.55,Default,del,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.82,0:10:10.04,Default,cor,0,0,0,,You've got to be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.82,0:10:10.04,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,いい加減にしろよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.39,0:10:12.03,Default,cor,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.39,0:10:12.03,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,どういうつもりなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.03,0:10:14.10,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Going after the guy's family...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.03,0:10:14.10,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,家族にまで手を出すなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.03,0:10:17.96,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Isn't your revenge against the Vanettis?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.03,0:10:17.96,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,復讐の相手はバネッチィのやつらだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:22.93,Default,cor,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:22.93,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,なんだ これ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.52,0:10:25.34,Default,av,0,0,0,,You wanted to go to college, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.52,0:10:25.34,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,学校 行きたっかたんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.61,0:10:28.15,Default,av,0,0,0,,Stay out of my life from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.61,0:10:28.15,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,もう 俺に関わるな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:35.28,Default,cor,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're{\i0} the one who dragged {\i1}me{\i0} into this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:35.28,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,お前が巻き込んだじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.02,0:10:53.25,Default,kid,0,0,0,,Where's my teddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.02,0:10:53.25,通用720日文-ja,kid,0,0,0,,テディは
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:56.01,Default,kid,0,0,0,,Hey, where'd my teddy go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:56.01,通用720日文-ja,kid,0,0,0,,{\an8}ね デディどこに行ったか知らない...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.56,0:10:54.47,Overlap,del,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.56,0:10:54.47,通用720日文-ja,del,0,0,0,,もしもし
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:56.87,Overlap,man,0,0,0,,Call off the investigation at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:56.87,通用720日文-ja,man,0,0,0,,今すぐ捜査を中止しろ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.19,0:11:00.16,Default,del,0,0,0,,I won't respond to threats!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.19,0:11:00.16,通用720日文-ja,del,0,0,0,,私には脅しには屈しない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.38,0:11:02.97,Default,man,0,0,0,,This is your last warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.38,0:11:02.97,通用720日文-ja,man,0,0,0,,最後の忠告だ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:03.78,Default,del,0,0,0,,I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:03.78,通用720日文-ja,del,0,0,0,,断る
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.78,0:11:05.50,Default,del,0,0,0,,Don't make me say it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.78,0:11:05.50,通用720日文-ja,del,0,0,0,,何度も言わせるな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.15,0:11:10.82,Default,wife,0,0,0,,You work too much, dear.\N You should take some time off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.15,0:11:10.82,通用720日文-ja,wife,0,0,0,,あなた働き過ぎよ 少しは休んで
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.82,0:11:11.64,Default,del,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:13.11,Default,del,0,0,0,,Take care of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:13.11,通用720日文-ja,del,0,0,0,,頼んだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.11,0:11:13.78,Default,cop,0,0,0,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.11,0:11:13.78,通用720日文-ja,cop,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.38,0:11:17.43,Default,kid,0,0,0,,Papa, aren't you coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.38,0:11:17.43,通用720日文-ja,kid,0,0,0,,パパ来ないの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.10,0:11:20.96,Default,del,0,0,0,,Do what your mom tells you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.10,0:11:20.96,通用720日文-ja,del,0,0,0,,母さんの言うこと よく聞くんだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.92,0:11:27.39,Default,wife,0,0,0,,We'll get going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.92,0:11:27.39,通用720日文-ja,wife,0,0,0,,もう行くわね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.39,0:11:28.22,Default,del,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:41.16,Default,del,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:41.16,通用720日文-ja,del,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.98,0:12:19.85,Default,fan,0,0,0,,You're sure about that info?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.98,0:12:19.85,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,その情報は確かなんだろうな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:23.06,Default,fan,0,0,0,,You surprised me, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:23.06,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,しかし驚きだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.50,0:12:27.42,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Never thought you'd come to me with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.50,0:12:27.42,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,まさかお前から こんな話が聞けるとはなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:34.06,Default,shop,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:34.06,通用720日文-ja,shop,0,0,0,,ったく
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.18,0:12:37.54,Default,shop,0,0,0,,This is how it always ends up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.18,0:12:37.54,通用720日文-ja,shop,0,0,0,,結局いつもこうなるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.48,0:12:41.54,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Delphy's taken care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.48,0:12:41.54,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,デルフィの件は片付いた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.54,0:12:43.32,Default,bar,0,0,0,,They'll leave the Lodge alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.54,0:12:43.32,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,ロッジにも目を瞑ると
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.32,0:12:43.98,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:47.49,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Can't believe they called us out\N here just to check the carpet color.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:47.49,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,わざわざ呼び出されてカーペットの色かよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.51,0:12:54.12,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.56,0:12:55.87,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Don't come any closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.56,0:12:55.87,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,それ以上近寄るな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.40,0:12:59.12,Default,man,0,0,0,,Hey... You're Nero Vanetti, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.40,0:12:59.12,通用720日文-ja,man,0,0,0,,あの ネロ ヴァネッティさんですよね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.54,0:13:01.75,Default,man,0,0,0,,I'm such a fan of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.54,0:13:01.75,通用720日文-ja,man,0,0,0,,俺 あんたのファンなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.00,0:13:04.92,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah? Glad to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.00,0:13:04.92,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,そうかい そいつありがとうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.36,0:13:08.31,Default,man,0,0,0,,Wait... Come on, hear me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.36,0:13:08.31,通用720日文-ja,man,0,0,0,,ちょっと なぁ 話聞いてくれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.31,0:13:10.81,Default,man,0,0,0,,Let me join the family! Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.31,0:13:10.81,通用720日文-ja,man,0,0,0,,俺をファミリーに入れてくれ ねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.81,0:13:12.37,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Hey! Take a hike.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.81,0:13:12.37,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,おぃ さっさと消えろう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.37,0:13:15.04,Default,man,0,0,0,,Come on, don't brush me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.37,0:13:15.04,通用720日文-ja,man,0,0,0,,そんな冷てぇこと言わねぇでよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.97,0:13:25.73,Default,av,0,0,0,,Nero!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.97,0:13:25.73,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,ネロ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.53,0:13:47.81,Default,tig,0,0,0,,It's Fango!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.53,0:13:47.81,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,ファンゴだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.30,0:13:50.27,Default,tig,0,0,0,,He set the whole thing up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.30,0:13:50.27,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,とうとう仕掛けてきやがった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.63,0:13:56.33,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Very few people knew Nero would be here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.63,0:13:56.36,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,しかし 今日ネロがここに来ることを知っていたのは限られた人間だけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.37,0:14:01.65,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Find the traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.37,0:14:01.65,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,探せ 裏切り者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.88,0:14:04.41,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.88,0:14:04.41,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,落ち着け
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.00,0:14:06.88,Default,cor,0,0,0,,How can I calm down?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.00,0:14:06.88,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,落ち着ける訳無いだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.88,0:14:09.76,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Listen up, Corty-baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.88,0:14:09.76,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,いいかコルテオちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.76,0:14:13.34,Default,fan,0,0,0,,We'd love to take you in at our place,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.76,0:14:13.34,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,お前をうちで匿うのは お安い御用だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.99,0:14:15.42,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,でもよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.99,0:14:18.54,Default,fan,0,0,0,,but then they'd know you're the one who betrayed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.42,0:14:18.84,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,それじゃ裏切り者がお前だってばれちまう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.94,0:14:22.79,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Drink some of this and calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.94,0:14:22.79,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,これでも飲んで落ち着け
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.17,0:14:32.68,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,俺達は次こそネロをやる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.17,0:14:35.26,Default,fan,0,0,0,,We'll kill Nero next time. \NThen the Vanettis will be through.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.68,0:14:35.26,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,そしたらヴァネッティは終わりだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.18,0:14:39.84,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,お前はうちで酒を作って がっぽり稼げばいい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.18,0:14:41.75,Default,fan,0,0,0,,You can make booze with us and make loads of cash. Everybody's happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.84,0:14:41.75,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,皆パッピーだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:45.24,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:45.24,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,ハッピー?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.24,0:14:47.94,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Yeah... Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.24,0:14:47.94,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,そう パーピー
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.30,0:14:52.49,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Show a little enthusiasm, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.30,0:14:52.49,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,乗り悪いな ボーイ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.78,0:14:56.55,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Anyway, about the booze...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.78,0:14:56.55,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,あ それで良い 酒のことなんだが
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.99,0:14:59.35,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Hey, you gonna walk home?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.99,0:14:59.35,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,おぃ 歩いて帰るのか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.84,0:15:05.25,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Everyone only cares about themselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.84,0:15:05.25,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,どいつも こいつも 自分のことばっかだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.43,0:15:17.75,Default,nero,0,0,0,,So this is what "high alert" looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.43,0:15:17.75,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,厳戒態勢ってやつか?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.47,0:15:21.85,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Hey, stop! You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.47,0:15:21.85,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,{\an8}ちょっと 駄目ですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.27,0:15:20.51,Overlap,gan,0,0,0,,Nero, it's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.27,0:15:20.51,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,ネロ 俺だ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.85,0:15:23.62,Default,gan,0,0,0,,I gotta talk to you! Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.85,0:15:23.62,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,話がある 開けろう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.28,0:15:29.36,Default,gan,0,0,0,,What is it, kid? I didn't come here to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.28,0:15:29.36,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,何だ 洟垂れ お前に用はねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.68,0:15:31.95,Default,av,0,0,0,,No one's allowed to see Nero right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.68,0:15:31.95,通用720日文-ja,av,0,0,0,,今は誰もネロとは会えない
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:35.24,Default,gan,0,0,0,,Listen, kid. How many years do you think I've been here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:35.24,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,おぃ ガキ 俺がここに何年いると思ってんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.24,0:15:36.86,Default,gan,0,0,0,,Before Nero was even born—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.24,0:15:36.86,通用720日文-ja,gan,0,0,0,,ネロが生まれる前...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.04,0:15:36.86,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,{\an8}叔父貴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:36.86,Overlap,bar,0,0,0,,Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.14,0:15:40.91,Default,bar,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.14,0:15:40.91,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,申し訳ありません
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:52.09,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Don't let anyone in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:52.09,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,誰も入れるなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.74,0:16:06.63,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Corteo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.74,0:16:06.63,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,コルテオ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.60,0:16:13.93,Default,bar,0,0,0,,We're done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.60,0:16:13.93,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,参ったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.93,0:16:16.80,Default,bar,0,0,0,,We won't be able to come back here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.93,0:16:16.80,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,しばらく ここへ顔を出せそうにない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.14,0:16:20.71,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Well? Did you find who did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.14,0:16:20.71,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,どう 目星はついたの
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.94,0:16:24.06,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Everyone's a suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.94,0:16:24.06,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,まあ 全員が容疑者みたいなもんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.78,0:16:26.16,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Me and you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.78,0:16:26.16,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,俺とお前もなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.27,0:16:31.02,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Well, you can leave this place to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.27,0:16:31.02,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,まあ ここは僕に任せてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.02,0:16:32.61,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Sure, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.02,0:16:32.61,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,あぁ 助かるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.61,0:17:13.55,Default,tig,0,0,0,,Learn everyone's names. That's the first step.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.61,0:17:13.55,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,名前を覚えわ 先ずそっからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:14.34,Default,man,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:14.34,通用720日文-ja,man,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.66,0:17:16.93,Default,tig,0,0,0,,If you need to piss, knock.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.66,0:17:16.93,通用720日文-ja,tig,0,0,0,,小便行きたくなったら ノックだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.66,0:17:19.56,Default,nero,0,0,0,,Is this the list of invitees?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.66,0:17:19.56,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,招待客の名簿は
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.56,0:17:22.76,Default,bar,0,0,0,,All of them, excluding those who haven't replied yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.56,0:17:22.76,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,向こうの返事待ちを除けばこれで全部だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.76,0:17:25.78,Default,nero,0,0,0,,I don't recognize most of them. Will it be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.76,0:17:25.78,通用720日文-ja,nero,0,0,0,,知らね名前だらけだ 大丈夫なのか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.12,0:17:27.84,Default,bar,0,0,0,,I vetted them before inviting them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.12,0:17:27.84,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,ちゃんと調べて呼んでる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.05,0:17:29.19,Default,bar,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.05,0:17:29.19,通用720日文-ja,bar,0,0,0,,心配するな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.18,0:17:39.56,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.18,0:17:39.56,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,どうだぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.72,0:17:42.10,Default,cer,0,0,0,,N-Nice swing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.72,0:17:42.10,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,ナイス スイングです
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:46.21,Default,fan,0,0,0,,I meant Corteo! Has he sent anymore info on Nero?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:46.21,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,コルテオのことだ ネロの情報が来たか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:48.57,Default,cer,0,0,0,,Sorry, sir... Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:48.57,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,すいあせん まだ何も
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.47,0:17:54.26,Default,lac,0,0,0,,Darling, you have an unusual visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.47,0:17:54.26,通用720日文-ja,lac,0,0,0,,ダーリン 珍しいお客よ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:17:59.22,Default,fan,0,0,0,,You're still in this town?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:17:59.22,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,まだこの町にいたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.22,0:18:01.64,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Thought you got replaced as head of the Bureau.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.22,0:18:01.64,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,元取締官殿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.13,0:18:06.02,Default,scu,0,0,0,,Thank you for asking. I've been reinstated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.13,0:18:06.02,通用720日文-ja,scu,0,0,0,,お陰様で 復職することになりましてね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.40,0:18:10.30,Default,scu,0,0,0,,What a surprise. Is that you, Cerotto?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.40,0:18:10.30,通用720日文-ja,scu,0,0,0,,驚いたなあ チェロットじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.30,0:18:12.24,Default,cer,0,0,0,,N-Nice to see you, Mr. Scusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.30,0:18:12.24,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,ど...どうも スクーザさん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.92,0:18:15.12,Default,scu,0,0,0,,So you were here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.92,0:18:15.46,通用720日文-ja,scu,0,0,0,,ここにいたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:18.10,Default,cer,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:18.10,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,え ええ まあ...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.64,0:18:22.38,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Good stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.64,0:18:22.38,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,気に入ったぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.40,0:18:26.58,Default,scu,0,0,0,,Well? What are you going to do about Corteo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.40,0:18:26.58,通用720日文-ja,scu,0,0,0,,で コルテオの方はどうするんです
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.84,0:18:29.50,Default,fan,0,0,0,,He knows entirely too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.84,0:18:29.50,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,あいつは色々知り過ぎだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.26,0:18:38.68,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Why's he calling me out here at this time of night?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.26,0:18:38.68,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,こんな時間に呼び出してなんの用だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:44.36,Default,cor,0,0,0,,You're being awfully quiet tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:44.36,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,今夜はやけに静かじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.41,0:18:48.91,Default,cer,0,0,0,,The city's gotten too dangerous lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.41,0:18:48.91,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,最近 この町も物騒んなってきたよなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.80,0:18:54.80,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,このままシカゴにでも行っちまうか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.96,0:18:54.80,Default,cer,0,0,0,,Hey, you want to just go to Chicago?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.14,0:18:57.70,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,禁止法もあるし
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.14,0:19:00.74,Default,cer,0,0,0,,Prohibition's on the way out. As long as we have the recipe, it'll take no time to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:19:00.74,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,レシピさえありゃ あっという間に...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.56,0:19:04.39,Default,cor,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.56,0:19:04.39,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,一体何の話だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.64,0:19:10.50,Default,cer,0,0,0,,It's no use. You stink to high heaven of booze.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.64,0:19:10.50,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,だめだ 酒臭くてたまんなねわ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.29,0:19:12.89,Default,cer,0,0,0,,You're gonna get {\i1}me{\i0} drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.29,0:19:12.89,通用720日文-ja,cer,0,0,0,,こっちは酔っちまうぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:29.22,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Welcome to my castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:29.46,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,ウェルカム トゥ マイ キャッスル
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.09,0:19:32.08,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Well? Want a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.09,0:19:32.08,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,どうだい 一杯やるか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.71,0:19:36.27,Default,cor,0,0,0,,What did you want to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.71,0:19:36.27,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,その 話って...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.92,0:19:38.62,Default,fan,0,0,0,,I'll keep it brief.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.92,0:19:38.62,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,簡潔に話そう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.39,0:19:43.64,Default,fan,0,0,0,,I'm through working with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.39,0:19:43.64,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,俺はお前と組むのをやめた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.48,0:19:51.15,Default,fan,0,0,0,,To be frank, I've got no more use for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.48,0:19:51.15,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,正直言ってお前にはもう使い道がない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.22,0:19:56.90,Default,cor,0,0,0,,But... my alcohol?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.22,0:19:56.90,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,でも酒は
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.74,0:19:59.77,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Didn't you want my alcohol?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.74,0:19:59.77,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,僕の酒が欲しいんじゃねえのか?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.40,0:20:03.68,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Have a drink first and calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.40,0:20:04.08,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,先ず一杯飲んで落ち着き
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.06,0:20:12.65,Default,cor,0,0,0,,Lawless Heaven?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.06,0:20:12.65,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,ローレス ヘブン
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.38,0:20:14.31,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.38,0:20:14.31,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,ほら
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.94,0:20:18.69,Default,cor,0,0,0,,The recipe...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.94,0:20:18.69,通用720日文-ja,cor,0,0,0,,レシピ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.00,0:20:19.94,Default,fan,0,0,0,,It was Scusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.00,0:20:20.42,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,スクーザだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:24.32,Default,fan,0,0,0,,He copied it from what that big-nose confiscated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:24.32,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,奴は鼻デカが押収した時に書き写したんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.32,0:20:27.96,Default,fan,0,0,0,,He even made me a real nice sample.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.32,0:20:27.96,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,そしてご丁寧にサンプルまで造ってきやがった
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.34,0:20:33.15,Default,fan,0,0,0,,You can't beat that kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.34,0:20:33.15,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,このキックはまさにだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.22,0:20:40.78,Default,fan,0,0,0,,But seriously, that guy is human garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.22,0:20:40.78,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,しかしおよ アイツ本当人間のクズだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.45,0:20:45.39,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Tried to charge me out the nose for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.45,0:20:45.39,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,こいつをとんでもない高値で売りつけてきやがって
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.98,0:20:52.30,Default,fan,0,0,0,,The point is, I don't need you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.98,0:20:52.30,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,まあ とにかく もうお前なんてどうでもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.96,0:21:24.67,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Forget it, just get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.96,0:21:24.67,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,まあいいや さっさと消えろ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.45,0:21:31.69,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll tell Nero-baby who the real traitor is instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.45,0:21:31.69,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,その代わり裏切り者の正体をネロちゃんに教えてあげるかなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.44,0:21:42.73,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Hey, operator! Get me the Vanetti mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.44,0:21:42.73,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,おう 交換手 バネッチィの屋敷だ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.73,0:21:45.43,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Put me through to Nero Vanetti.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.73,0:21:45.43,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,ネロ バネッチィに繋いでくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.38,0:21:50.24,Default,fan,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.38,0:21:50.24,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,何だ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.98,0:21:55.62,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Me? My name is Fango!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.98,0:21:55.62,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,俺? 俺の名前はファンゴだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.80,0:22:12.88,Default,fan,0,0,0,,Where'd you go? Can't see...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.80,0:22:12.88,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,どこへ行った 見えね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.74,0:22:18.25,Default,fan,0,0,0,,That feels pretty damn good, boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.74,0:22:18.25,通用720日文-ja,fan,0,0,0,,気持ちいいじゃねえか ボーイ
